Verification
Verify Istio Installation
kubectl get pods -n istio-system
istioctl version
Expected output: All pods running, client and control plane versions match.

Verify Sidecar Injection
kubectl get pods -n microservices -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}{"\t"}{.spec.containers[*].name}{"\n"}{end}'
Expected output: Each pod should show two containers (app + istio-proxy).

Verify Traffic Routing
# Test traffic distribution
for i in {1..20}; do curl -s http://$GATEWAY_URL | grep -o "v[12]"; done | sort | uniq -c
Expected output: Distribution should match your configured weights.

